<item>
            <title>[SOLR-6057] Duplicate background-color in #content #analysis #analysis-result .match (analysis.css)</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-6057</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Inside of solr/webapp/web/css/styles/analysis.css, you can find #content #analysis #analysis-result .match element with following content:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;	#content #analysis #analysis-result .match&lt;/p&gt;
 	{
 	background-color: #e9eff7;
 	background-color: #f2f2ff;
 	}

&lt;p&gt;background-color listed twice.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Also, it was very hard for me to see the highlight. Recommend to change it to background-color: #FF0000;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
